Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:53.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fax-0.1}想い出はモノクローム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.11,0:22:58.36,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}色を点けてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:06.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}もう一度そばに来て
